# TIRTC Color Palette

## Tailwind Tokens (use these in className)

### Primary (Blue)
| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `primary-900` | `#1E3A8A` | Deep navy — headings, dark surfaces |
| `primary-700` | `#1D4ED8` | Main blue — buttons, links, icons |
| `primary-500` | `#3B82F6` | Hover / lighter accents |

### Secondary (Orange)
| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `secondary-600` | `#EA580C` | CTA hover |
| `secondary-500` | `#F97316` | Primary CTA buttons |
| `secondary-400` | `#FB923C` | Lighter accents |

### Accent (Cyan)
| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `accent-500` | `#06B6D4` | Step numbers, tech vibe, ecosystem cards |
| `accent-400` | `#22D3EE` | Lighter cyan |

### Backgrounds
| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `bg-background-primary` | `#FFFFFF` | Main page, cards |
| `bg-background-secondary` | `#F8FAFC` | Alternate sections |
| `bg-background-muted` | `#F1F5F9` | Cards, muted blocks |

### Text / Content
| Token | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `text-content-primary` | `#0F172A` | Main text (almost black) |
| `text-content-secondary` | `#475569` | Paragraph text |
| `text-content-muted` | `#94A3B8` | Labels, captions |

## Section Alternation Pattern
```
Hero         → gradient (#1D4ED8 → #0891B2)
Partners     → bg-background-secondary
About        → bg-background-primary
Problem/Sol  → bg-background-muted
Courses      → bg-background-primary
How It Works → bg-background-secondary
Model        → bg-background-primary
Leadership   → bg-background-muted
CTA          → bg-background-primary
Contact      → bg-background-muted
Footer       → bg-content-primary (#0F172A)
```

## MUI Theme Mapping
`theme.ts` palette:
- `primary.main` = `#1D4ED8`, `primary.dark` = `#1E3A8A`, `primary.light` = `#3B82F6`
- `secondary.main` = `#F97316`, `secondary.dark` = `#EA580C`, `secondary.light` = `#FB923C`
- `accent.main` = `#06B6D4`
- `text.primary` = `#0F172A`, `text.secondary` = `#475569`, `text.disabled` = `#94A3B8`
- `background.paper` = `#FFFFFF`, `background.default` = `#F8FAFC`
